stories.title: More than half your body is not human [2018]

stories.text:
Anyone else from New Zealand getting this issue?

google Cloud contacted me this morning to let me know my payment via CC failed. Card is valid.

I've contacted the bank, says others are experiencing the same, so I plugged in my cc from another bank.

I've tried with 2 cards from 2 banks, seems both fail. error: They provided the following reason: Unfortunately, they didn't give us a reason why. Check with them for more information.

The call centre agent was quite happy to hear that it wasn't only her banks cards.

Anyone at google know what's happening?
